text: Macrozamia lomandroides is a species of plant in the family Zamiaceae. It is endemic to Australia. Its natural habitat is subtropical or tropical dry forests. ==References== lomandroides Category:Vulnerable flora of Australia Category:Nature Conservation Act endangered biota Category:Vulnerable biota of Queensland Category:Endangered flora of Australia Category:Flora of Queensland Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
